Package com.collabnet.ccf.core.ga

Class Summary
AttachmentMetaData The class AttachmentMetaData contains the fields of the attachment GenericArtifact along with the possbile values for AttachmnetType and AttachmentValueType.
GenericArtifact This is the root element for every entity that is transported through the CCF pipeline.
GenericArtifactField A field has a name and a field type and contains a typed value for the property of the artifact that is described by this field.
GenericArtifactHelper This class helps to generate and parse the schema defined generic xml artifact format
